<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f0f4f8; padding: 24px; color: #1a202c; margin: 0; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 40px; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .logo { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #8b5cf6); border-radius: 8px; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; padding: 6px 14px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    h1 { color: #0d1b2a; font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .subtitle { color: #64748b; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 28px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .themes { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .badge { background: #e0f7ff; color: #0077aa; border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px 14px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
    .section { margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .summary-box { background: #f8fafc; border-left: 4px solid #00d4ff; padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; white-space: pre-line; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8; color: #1a202c; }
    .contact-block { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; }
    .contact-line { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: #1a202c; }
    .contact-line:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    a { color: #0077aa; text-decoration: none; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 28px 0; }
    .footer { font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo">CP</div>

    <h1>Bonjour <%= @name %>,</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Votre demande a bien été reçue. Je vous recontacte sous 24h pour convenir d'un premier échange.
    </p>

    <div class="themes">
      <% @themes.each do |theme| %>
        <span class="badge"><%= theme %></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="label">Résumé de votre demande</div>
      <div class="summary-box"><%= @summary %></div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="label">Mes coordonnées</div>
      <div class="contact-block">
        <div class="contact-line"><strong>Cyrille PIERRE</strong> — Consultant Indépendant</div>
        <div class="contact-line">Ingénieur Arts & Métiers · Lyon</div>
        <div class="contact-line">📧 <a href="mailto:cyrille.pierre@gmail.com">cyrille.pierre@gmail.com</a></div>
        <div class="contact-line">📞 06 18 02 24 52</div>
        <div class="contact-line">🔗 <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cyrille-pierre">linkedin.com/in/cyrille-pierre</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="footer">
      Ce message a été envoyé depuis <a href="https://cyrillepierre.fr">cyrillepierre.fr</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
